+        //   alpha[1][3] = (alpha[0][2]+alpha[0][3])*P(a,1) but alpha[0][2]=alpha[0][3]=-inf -> -inf
+        //   So alpha[1][3] = alpha[1][2]*P(a,2) + alpha[1][3] (skip not allowed since labels[3]=labels[1]=a)
+        //   Wait, let me recompute with the lattice definition
